            "critical_success": "The creature is unaffected.",
            "success": "Powder sticks to the target, causing it to leave behind telltale footprints. Being \ninvisible\n makes the target \nhidden\n, rather than \nundetected\n, to creatures that could see it if it weren't invisible.",
